00:04:55.980 --> 00:05:00.919
Now it’s broken up in a category so accessories,
clothing, drink, grooming, shoes…

00:05:00.919 --> 00:05:04.740
…too expensive travel, watches, women, etcetera.

00:05:04.740 --> 00:05:09.570
This is one of the – I think the weak points
about dappered.com is that some of these – a

00:05:09.570 --> 00:05:11.120
